{"tid":2231760,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美軍考慮與馬斯克合作開發最高效能的全球定位系統","createTime":"2020-10-06T01:52:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T17:50:58.000Z","uid":295230,"like":94,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"1292793f6a2803defad08056aeb481fd65e3fe09","tid":2231760,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T01:52:59.000Z","msg":"<strong>美國陸軍想與「星鏈」衛星網合作</strong><br />\n<br />\n美國陸軍已將目光投向SpaceX公司的「星鏈」衛星網(Starlink constellation)上，SpaceX公司在地球外的軌道上已經有700多顆衛星，且馬斯克放話說預計會發射更多衛星也是眾所皆知的事情。根據《麻省理工技術評論》(MIT Technology Review)報導，SpaceX發射「星鏈」(Starlink)的目的是讓互聯網與整個地球相互連接起來，但現在美國軍方想對這些衛星進行改造，美軍想用這些衛星來創建一個堪稱比全球定位系統(GPS)更好、更安全的導航網絡。"},{"pid":"f18fd8f24daa5ce0692cf2e798631faf97d0637f","tid":2231760,"uid":295230,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T01:53:03.000Z","msg":"好期待Starlink IPO<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a05c1c38e1ec5f083862640fa9924808d8cfba35","tid":2231760,"uid":224479,"like":49,"dislike":1,"score":48,"quote":{"pid":"f18fd8f24daa5ce0692cf2e798631faf97d0637f","tid":2231760,"uid":295230,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T01:53:03.000Z","msg":"好期待Starlink IPO<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T01:55:37.000Z","msg":"希望 elon musk 用自己個名整一間公司 包晒所有佢啲公司<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />all in"},{"pid":"3356eed79c7a4eeca856282c78ce4ac1ba53689b","tid":2231760,"uid":38982,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T01:56:01.000Z","msg":"美軍係咪為MQ9無人機血滴子更加精準而鋪路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji